 391, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"its normal state\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is also the Sunnah or tradition of the Prophet Muhammad (PBUH) that this helps blood flow better, using cups to draw fluid into the skin and animal horns can also be used.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunnah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunnah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunnah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunnah\"}, {\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_honorifics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"PBUH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_honorifics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_honorifics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tradition\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"the Prophet Muhammad\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"cups\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"fluid\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"animal horns\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A vacuum pulls the skin up into the cups.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A vacuum\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"the cups\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This breaks the capillaries in the skin, causing the bruise-like effect seen on swimmers.\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the capillaries\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"the bruise-like effect\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vacuum can be created with a flame or suction.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vacuum\", \"score\": 0.9756423625958403, \"rank\": 0.02496574394004912, \"text\": \"Vacuum\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vacuum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vacuum\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a flame\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"suction\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cups remain in place for 5 to 15 minutes.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cups\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"5 to 15 minutes\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This draws more blood to the area, helping it to heal and break up scar tissue.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more blood\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"scar tissue\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are two types of cupping: wet and dry.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two types\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"cupping\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In wet cupping, small cuts are made to draw blood or fluid from the body.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wet cupping\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"small cuts\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"fluid\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dry cupping does not draw blood, but can be combined with massage.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dry cupping\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"massage\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Hadith (saying) of the Prophet (PBUH) as narrated by one of his companions, Jabir bin 'Abdullah, emphasizes the importance of cupping.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hadith\", \"score\": 0.9999999958595254, \"rank\": 4.138982706350298e-09, \"text\": \"Hadith\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hadith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hadith\"}, {\"begin\": 1183, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdullah_ibn_Abd_al-Muttalib\", \"score\": 0.9998335467072221, \"rank\": 0.00016633269991681048, \"text\": \"Abdullah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdullah_ibn_Abd_al-Muttalib\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdullah_ibn_Abd_al-Muttalib\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Prophet\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"(PBUH\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"his companions\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"Jabir bin\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jabir bin 'Abdullah said: \\\"I will not leave until he is cupped, for I heard the Prophet (PBUH) say, 'There is healing in cupping.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdullah_ibn_Abd_al-Muttalib\", \"score\": 0.9998335467072221, \"rank\": 0.00016633269991681048, \"text\": \"Abdullah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdullah_ibn_Abd_al-Muttalib\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdullah_ibn_Abd_al-Muttalib\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jabir bin\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\"